From: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
Date: Thu, 09 Jul 2026 18:54:48 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] refactor: For compliance with the BC Society Act, drop direct references to the member count

Signed-off-by: Felicitas Pojtinger <felicitas@pojtinger.com>
